This is not an equality! There must be a mistake in my reasoning.

Wait, the natural transformation is from `G ‚ąė ŌÄ‚āā` to `F ‚ąė ŌÄ‚āĀ`. So the map should be `NatTrans : (G ‚ąė ŌÄ‚āā) ‚Üí (F ‚ąė ŌÄ‚āĀ)`.
